  "root_text": {
    "an7.20:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7.20 ",
    "an7.20:0.2": "2. Anusayavagga ",
    "an7.20:0.3": "Niddasavatthusutta ",
    "an7.20:1.1": "“Sattimāni, bhikkhave, niddasavatthūni. ",
    "an7.20:1.2": "Katamāni satta? ",
    "an7.20:1.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhāsamādāne tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca sikkhāsamādāne avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.4": "dhammanisantiyā tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca dhammanisantiyā avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.5": "icchāvinaye tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca icchāvinaye avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.6": "paṭisallāne tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca paṭisallāne avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.7": "vīriyārambhe tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca vīriyārambhe avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.8": "satinepakke tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca satinepakke avigatapemo, ",
    "an7.20:1.9": "diṭṭhipaṭivedhe tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca diṭṭhipaṭivedhe avigatapemo. ",
    "an7.20:1.10": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, satta niddasavatthūnī”ti. ",
    "an7.20:1.11": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "an7.20:1.12": "Anusayavaggo dutiyo. ",
    "an7.20:2.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "an7.20:2.1": "Duve anusayā kulaṁ, ",
    "an7.20:2.2": "Puggalaṁ udakūpamaṁ; ",
    "an7.20:2.3": "Aniccaṁ dukkhaṁ anattā ca, ",
    "an7.20:2.4": "Nibbānaṁ niddasavatthu cāti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an7.20:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 7.20 ",
    "an7.20:0.2": "2. Tendencies ",
    "an7.20:0.3": "Qualifications for Graduation ",
    "an7.20:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these seven qualifications for graduation. ",
    "an7.20:1.2": "What seven? ",
    "an7.20:1.3": "It’s when a mendicant has a keen enthusiasm to undertake the training … ",
    "an7.20:1.4": "to examine the teachings … ",
    "an7.20:1.5": "to get rid of desires … ",
    "an7.20:1.6": "for retreat … ",
    "an7.20:1.7": "to rouse up energy … ",
    "an7.20:1.8": "for mindfulness and alertness … ",
    "an7.20:1.9": "to penetrate theoretically. And they don’t lose these desires in the future. ",
    "an7.20:1.10": "These are the seven qualifications for graduation.” ",
